@project1of1 I rate the originality behind the ideas you have but sometimes I feel like there's a little bit too much going on. I my opinion you should try use a single standout piece and work around that. By over complicating the design of each piece I feel like when combined in a whole outfit there are too many conflicting ideas that are trying to fight each other if you understand what I'm saying. Try using certain colour schemes that enhance each other as well eg complementary, triadic, analogous. I too want to become a designer in the future so I completely understand it but in my opinion sometimes understated pieces make the standout pieces pop out and seem more appealing.
